data.title: St. Stanislaus Elementary School
data.meta_description: St. Stanislaus - St. Stanislaus Elementary School page
data.text:
St. Stanislaus Elementary School has a long tradition of high quality education. We have a 100% graduation rate from the eighth grade. We currently have 260 students in grades K-8, and multiple classes for some grades.

Our programs benefit the development of the whole child. We assist each child in the development of his or her self image by developing programs that benefit each one's educational needs.

For more information visit the school website. This will take you away from the parish website so be certain to press back in your browser after visiting the website.

http://www.saintstanislaus.us/
